==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Movie
<hw>Mov"ie</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A motion
picture.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> film, picture, moving picture, motion picture,
picture show, flick.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A motion picture show; the event of showing a motion
picture. In the <pluf>pl.</pluf>, the event of showing a motion picture
at a movie theater; <as>as, to go to the <ex>movies</ex>; to spend an
evening at the <ex>movies</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <pluf>pl.</pluf> <def>The motion picture industry or
medium, generally.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Moving</ent>⟦br⟧
